63
00:03:23.029 --> 00:03:27.713
But,
&gt;&gt; Brian Holt: And then you see here,

64
00:03:27.713 --> 00:03:28.869
there is a semicolon.

65
00:03:28.869 --> 00:03:32.982
That's just punctuation in CSS,
it's saying I am done with this sentence.

66
00:03:32.982 --> 00:03:37.689
This really is like a period or
a full stop for CSS.

67
00:03:37.689 --> 00:03:41.638
At the end of every line, you just
put a semicolon to say I'm done and

68
00:03:41.638 --> 00:03:43.664
I'm gonna go on to the next thing.

69
00:03:43.664 --> 00:03:44.684
It does have to be there.

70
00:03:49.990 --> 00:03:53.128
&gt;&gt; Brian Holt: So I can put a lot
