zero zero zero one miles tall, right?

78
00:04:22.961 --> 00:04:26.155
There's like many
different measurements for

79
00:04:26.155 --> 00:04:28.876
doing height just like there is for CSS.

80
00:04:28.876 --> 00:04:32.828
You can do it in pixels,
you can do it in EMs, you can do it in X,

81
00:04:32.828 --> 00:04:36.254
